      <title>特朗普胜选后抵押贷款债券仍有上涨空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/mortgage-bonds-have-room-to-run-after-decisive-trump-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新机构抵押贷款债券的风险溢价周三收紧，一些人认为，大选前该市场异常便宜，有望与美国股市和美元等货币一起受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/mortgage-bonds-have-room-to-run-after-decisive-trump-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 17:36:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
